{"tid":1212431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"無聊查左下，原來中國係聯合國人權理事會既任期今屆係2019年屆滿而且無得再連任住","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T18:38:50.000Z","uid":110259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09eac4eaffe14ecbf44cbcf84da1a443d964ca44","tid":1212431,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:38:50.000Z","msg":"我係度搵緊點搵國際人權組織同人權歷史個陣無意中發現<br />\n中國係2013－2016同2016－2019都做緊<br />\n而理事會成員國每屆任期3年，最多可連任一次。經三分之二成員國同意，聯合國大會可中止嚴重違反人權的國家的人權理事會成員資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%BC%9A#cite_note-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2581%2594%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259D%2583%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BC%259A%23cite_note-4&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=81226c3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%BC%9A#cite_note-4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/CH/HRBodies/HRC/Pages/CurrentMembers.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FCH%2FHRBodies%2FHRC%2FPages%2FCurrentMembers.aspx&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=3d85ebbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/CH/HRBodies/HRC/Pages/CurrentMembers.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇關係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}